OL,3,CPrisoner Governor temporarily stands
OL,4,Cdown as conduct investigation begins
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey has revealed
OL,7,Fthat the island's Prison Governor has
OL,8,Fstepped down temporarily due to
OL,9,Finvestigations into his conduct.
OL,11,FJohn De Carteret voluntarily decided
OL,12,Fto step aside after allegations about
OL,13,Fhis conduct came to light - which have
OL,14,Fnot been revealed.
OL,16,FMr De Carteret permanently took on the
OL,17,Frole in May 2020, following a nine-
OL,18,Fmonth stint as Acting Prison Governor.
