PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1775592346
OL,3,CPrisoner Governor temporarily stands
OL,4,Cdown as conduct investigation begins
OL,6,FThe decision was made in agreement
OL,7,Fwith the Committee for Home Affairs
OL,8,Fand the States Chief Executive & Head
OL,9,Fof the Public Service, Boley Smillie.
OL,11,FIt means that Deputy Governor Tracey
OL,12,FMahy will lead the prison operations
OL,13,Fin the interim.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Mr Smillie said:
OL,16,F"Matters will be investigated fully
OL,17,Fand fairly, and no one should draw any
OL,18,Fconclusion from the Prison Governor's
OL,19,Fdecision to temporarily step aside.
